sentences.english: Process flow of olefin conversion unit is introduced.
sentences.chinese: 對烯烴轉換工藝技術作了介紹。

sentences.english: The two main classes of petrochemicals are olefins and aromatics.
sentences.chinese: 石化的兩類主要產品是烯烴和芳烴。

sentences.english: In this paper, a kind of new catalysts for olefins hydroformylation was studied.
sentences.chinese: 本論文研製了一種新型烯烴氫甲酰化催化劑。

sentences.english: Polymers of vinyl chloride or of other halogenated olefins, in primary forms.
sentences.chinese: 初級形狀的氯乙烯或其他鹵化烯烴聚合物。

sentences.english: Optionally the olefinic naphtha has a low content of acids.
sentences.chinese: 任選地，所述烯烴石腦油含低含量的酸。

sentences.english: An unsaturated hydrocarbon belonging to the alkene homologous series.
sentences.chinese: 不飽和碳氫化合物，屬於烯烴同系物。

sentences.english: Compounds containing two double bonds are called dienes.
sentences.chinese: 包含兩個雙鍵的化合物叫做二烯烴。

sentences.english: A new direct hydration catalyst for preparing alcohols from dicyclopentadiene was studied.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一種烯烴水合制醇的新方法。

sentences.english: The product has good catalytic property for the formation of diene stereospecific polymers.
sentences.chinese: 製得的叔碳酸釹具有對二烯烴良好的定向聚合活性。

sentences.english: Firstly the dependence of stress strain behavior of polyolefin on the test conditions was investigated.
sentences.chinese: 首先研究了聚烯烴應力應變行爲的測試條件依賴性。

sentences.english: The suggestion for developing the technics of alkene preparation from natural gas in China was proposed.
sentences.chinese: 並對我國今後天然氣制烯烴技術的開發提出了建議。

sentences.english: Application and preparation of a non - hydrogenation reducing - olefin catalyst were introduced.
sentences.chinese: 介紹了一種非加氫降烯烴催化劑的製備及應用。

sentences.english: Application and preparation of a non-hydrogenation reducing-olefin catalyst were studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究了一種非加氫降烯烴催化劑的製備及應用。

sentences.english: Polymers of propylene or of other olefins, in primary forms.
sentences.chinese: 初級形狀的丙烯或其他烯烴聚合物。

sentences.english: The low-molecular-weight homolog III shows no difference in catalytic activity toward the two cycloalkenes.
sentences.chinese: 同源低分子量顯示使用的環烯烴無催化活性差異。

sentences.english: The invention relates to a preparation method of open-cell foamed polyolefin.
sentences.chinese: 本發明涉及一種開孔發泡聚烯烴的製備方法。
